ed editions","Stay agile and adaptable to ","last-minute changes"," and evolving business priorities"],"location":"selangor","jobType":"\n        Full Time","jobCategory":"459-transportation_logistic","datePosted":"\n          Posted\n          12 hours ago • Closing\n          5 Dec 2025\n        ","scrapedAt":1.745099271001824E9,"jobUrl":"https://www.ricebowl.my/job/22526468-procurement-executive","_type":"Job"}
